            <abstract>
                <p>Medical and magic prescriptions against migraine (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለራስ፡ ፍልፀት፡</foreign>), 
                    colic (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለሆድ፡ ቍርፀት፡</foreign>), čǝfe (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለችፌ፡</foreign>),
                    for love (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለፍቅር፡</foreign>), 
                    against pain in urination (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለሽንት፡ ምጽ፡</foreign>),
                    for becoming rich (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለአስተጋብኦ፡ ንዋይ፡</foreign>), 
                    against thieves working through magic (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለሰላቢ፡</foreign>),
                    against scrofula (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለነቀርሳ፡</foreign>), fever (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለንዳድ፡</foreign>),
                    for a success at the market (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለገ<sic>ብ</sic>ያ፡</foreign>),
                    against syphilis (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለቂጥኝ፡</foreign>),
                    the fall of the field (?), the birth of the Zār (?) (<foreign xml:lang="am">የሜዳ፡ ውድቀት፡ የዛር፡ ውላጅ፡</foreign>), 
                    albugo (<foreign xml:lang="am">ከዓይኑ፡ በጣለበት፡</foreign>), 
                    a hair growing [in the eye] (<foreign xml:lang="am">ጠጉር፡ ለበቀለበት፡</foreign>),
                    corrosive leprosy (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለደዌ፡ ሥጋ፡</foreign>),
                    and tapeworm (<foreign xml:lang="am">ኮሶ፡</foreign>),
                    if a horse grows thin (<foreign xml:lang="am">ፈረስ፡ እየከሳ፡</foreign>),
                    against baldness (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለቧሄ፡</foreign>),
                    pain in labour (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለምጽ፡</foreign>), the shadow (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለጥላ፡</foreign>), 
                    fire (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለእሳት፡</foreign>), snakebite (<foreign xml:lang="am">የእባብ፡ ለነከሰው፡</foreign>),
                    conjunctivitis (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለዓይን፡ ማዝ፡</foreign>), 
                    hemeralopy (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለዳፍንት፡</foreign>),
                    jaundice (<foreign xml:lang="am">ዖፍ፡ ለዛረችው፡</foreign>), 
                    ʾabrǝq, scrofula of a horse (<foreign xml:lang="am">የፈረስ፡ ነቀርሳ፡</foreign>),
                    rheumatism (<foreign xml:lang="am">ለቍርጥማት፡</foreign>) 
                    and the skin disease (<foreign xml:lang="am">መድየት፡</foreign>).</p>
